      <subsection name="OSGi packaging">
<p>
The <strong>jbundle OSGi to JNLP servlet</strong> is an <a href="http://www.osgi.org">OSGi</a> bundle.
To use it in your OSGi project, just install and start this bundle in your OSGi environment.
Remember to start a web server such as tomcat or jetty.
</p>
<p>
<code>
OBR Repository index:<br/>
${project.organization.url}/${OBRRepositoryIndex}<br/>
Manifest import:<br/>
Import-Package: ${project.artifactId};resolution:=optional;version=${project.version}
</code>
</p>
      </subsection>

